Author: scifichick774 <br>
Rating: PG-13 <br>
Category: Drama/Angst Chloe/Lucas at the beginning, Chloe/Lex eventually <br>
Spoilers: Past Dichotic <br>
Summary: Lucas's adoptive father moves him to Smallville after his wife's death. Lex learns the truth. <br>
