Author's Note: Many thanks to my betas Sarah and Mona. I know, I'm actually using betas for this one. You're in shock aren't you? Anyway, I have a bad feeling this is going to end up being a really angst-ridden fic. There will be some humor, but I just know it's going to be heart wrenching. Also, I may end up raising the rating down the road. Just warning you, so you can turn away if you want.<br>
