<br>
&quot;Why would I do that?&quot; He replied in a teasing tone. Chloe narrowed her eyes at him a little.<br>
<br>
&quot;Don't tease him Lex,&quot; Chloe warned. &quot;Not about this. He's actually concerned for some reason.&quot;<br>
<br>
