<br>
I can take care of myself.<br>
<br>
Im sure you can, but that doesnt remove my suit of armor.<br>
<br>
Suit of armor?  Chloe asked with one eyebrow raised high in the air. <br>
<br>
The knight in shining armor bit.  I came here with every intention to rescue you from your own stubbornness.<br>
<br>
I dont need rescuing Lex.  Contrary to popular belief, I am not one of the many Smallville damsels in distress.<br>
<br>
I didnt know such a group existed.<br>
<br>
Yes you did, Chloe argued.  Its just that no one ever gave it a name before.<br>
<br>
