Where is she?!<br>
<br>
Lionels head turned toward the sound of Lexs growl.<br>
<br>
I presume you mean Miss Sullivan? Lionel asked calmly and somewhat smugly.  <br>
<br>
He was taken by surprise when Lex shoved him against the wall, tipping over the decanter set which stood in the way.  If Lexs physical action hadnt been enough, the sound of glass breaking and the liquid running from the containers was more than enough to convince Lionel that Lex was very serious and he shouldnt treat whatever it was that Lex was upset about with only trivial concern.<br>
