<br>
I dont know what youre talking about, Lionel said, trying to remove Lexs hands from where they were clenching his shirt and jacket.  He failed.  Lex gave him another push, slamming his head back hard against the wall.<br>
<br>
I dont have time for your stupid games.  I was attacked by two men with a tranquilizer gun and when I woke up, Chloe had been taken.  The police are already looking for her, and Ive put up a reward for information as to her whereabouts.  Now - what have you done with Chloe?!<br>
