Lex ---<br>
<br>
I let you live once, Lex interrupted, it wont happen again.<br>
<br>
I dont have any idea where your girlfriend is, Lex, Lionel answered.  Lex narrowed his eyes at him and shook his head slightly, because it almost sounded like he was telling the truth.  In fact, if he hadnt been raised to be suspicious of everything that came out of Lionels mouth, then he would have believed him.  She *is* your girlfriend now, isnt she?<br>
