<br>
Chloe shot him a half-questioning, half-horrified look and Luke continued.<br>
<br>
Did you know that he gave me a rather sizeable amount of money to try and make me forget about you? Luke shook his head and let out a small sigh.  But I could never forget about you.  We belong together.<br>
